OL,3,G`````````````````````````````Sj]Q|T/G\`
OL,4,CWeekly Teletext Art challengeS #///'!  
OL,6, In February 2021, ZXGuesser started the
OL,7,F_WeeklyTeletextArtGactivity on Twitter 
OL,8, and Facebook.                          
OL,10, The goal of this hashtag was to promote
OL,11, teletext art and encourage everyone to 
OL,12, have a go by providing a weekly prompt.
OL,14, Subjects have included "Countryside",  
OL,15, "Dolphin and/or Microphone", "Circus", 
OL,16, "Spaceship", "Octopus and/or Suitcase",
OL,17, and many others.                       
